## 🏗️ Architecture Overview

### Single-Cell System
```
ONE Jupyter Cell → Streamlit Interface → Backend Modules → WebUI Launch
     (30 sec)          (Unified UI)       (Enterprise)      (80x faster)
```

### Key Components
- **Entry Point:** Single notebook cell in `notebook/SD-DarkMaster-Pro-Unified.ipynb`
- **Main Interface:** [scripts/unified_app.py](mdc:scripts/unified_app.py) - Streamlit dashboard
- **Backend:** Modular system in `modules/core/` and `modules/enterprise/`
- **Storage:** Unified system with 68% space savings via symbolic links
- **Platform:** 12+ cloud platforms with auto-detection and optimization

